          { "feature": "night_pain", "weight": 4 },
          { "feature": "fixed_deformity", "weight": 4 }
        ],
        "management": "Total hip arthroplasty (cemented/cementless/press-fit). Pre-op templating. Post-op: WBAT, hip precautions (no adduction/past 90 degrees flexion early)."
